                <div class="col-xs-12 no-margin"> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> 45 mins<br><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-stats"></span> calories: 369kcal. fat: 18g. carbohydrates: 21g. protein: 30g.</div>
